<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 22:07:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“罪犯声称皈依基督教，以避免被英国驱逐出境”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/murderers-rapists-avoiding-deportation-from-uk-after-jail-time-by-claiming-to-be-christian-converts-report/articleshow/107669625.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107669625.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据英国《泰晤士报》报道，杀人犯、强奸犯、恋童癖者和毒贩等在英国服刑后因声称皈依基督教而避免被驱逐出境的外国罪犯。外国公民在难民听证会上辩称，如果被驱逐出境，他们可能会因所谓的“皈依”而在本国面临迫害。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 18:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/murderers-rapists-avoiding-deportation-from-uk-after-jail-time-by-claiming-to-be-christian-converts-report/articleshow/107669625.cms</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，普京关于乌克兰停火的建议遭到美国拒绝</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putins-suggestion-of-ukraine-ceasefire-rejected-by-united-states-sources-say/articleshow/107668214.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107668214.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中间人在土耳其举行会议，讨论普京关于乌克兰停火的提议。杰克·沙利文、比尔·伯恩斯和安东尼·布林肯等美国高级官员参与了讨论。但由于美国坚持乌克兰参加，谈判未能成功。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 17:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putins-suggestion-of-ukraine-ceasefire-rejected-by-united-states-sources-say/articleshow/107668214.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国东北部遭遇暴风雪 1000多个航班取消</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/over-1000-flights-cancelled-as-heavy-snow-storm-hits-northeastern-us/articleshow/107668661.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107668661.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国东北部部分地区遭受暴风雪袭击，导致航班取消、道路湿滑以及学校上课时间中断。纽约市在线学习系统出现技术困难，影响了学生上课。超过 1,000 架航班被取消，主要是纽约市和波士顿的航班。据报道，发生了事故，导致一些州禁止某些车辆在高速公路上行驶。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 17:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/over-1000-flights-cancelled-as-heavy-snow-storm-hits-northeastern-us/articleshow/107668661.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普再次向最高法院寻求推迟对 1 月 6 日事件的起诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-goes-to-supreme-court-again-seeking-to-delay-prosecution-for-january-6-events/articleshow/107665617.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107665617.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普周一重返美国最高法院，寻求暂缓上诉法院允许对其试图推翻 2020 年选举结果进行刑事起诉的裁决。特朗普的法律团队以“这个申请再次似曾相识”开始他们的演讲，他们认为，如果总统在任期内可能因行为而面临刑事指控，可能会导致此类起诉的增加，从而造成破坏性的循环。互相指责。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 14:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-goes-to-supreme-court-again-seeking-to-delay-prosecution-for-january-6-events/articleshow/107665617.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯将爱沙尼亚总理列入通缉名单，罪名是“亵渎历史记忆”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-puts-estonian-pm-on-wanted-list-for-desecration-of-historical-memory/articleshow/107660433.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107660433.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯警方已将爱沙尼亚总理卡亚·卡拉斯、爱沙尼亚国务秘书泰马尔·彼得科普和立陶宛文化部长西蒙纳斯·凯里斯列入通缉名单，罪名是“亵渎历史记忆”和“毁坏苏联士兵纪念碑”。波罗的海国家计划拆除苏联时代的纪念碑。俄罗斯还通缉数十名波罗的海政客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-puts-estonian-pm-on-wanted-list-for-desecration-of-historical-memory/articleshow/107660433.cms</guid></item><item><title>塞内加尔暂停移动互联网</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mobile-internet-suspended-in-senegal/articleshow/107659643.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107659643.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塞内加尔通讯部表示，周二，塞内加尔的移动互联网接入被暂停，这是本月第二次。此前，当局禁止了反对推迟二月总统选举的游行。总统麦基·萨勒决定将 2 月 25 日的投票推迟到 12 月，这使塞内加尔陷入了一场危机，抗议者与安全部队之间的冲突已造成三人死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mobile-internet-suspended-in-senegal/articleshow/107659643.cms</guid></item><item><title>从国外来看，巴基斯坦选举令人失望，加剧了不稳定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/seen-from-abroad-pakistan-elections-disappoint-add-to-instability/articleshow/107657523.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107657523.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;外交政策分析人士表示，巴基斯坦最近的选举结果令许多外国合作伙伴和竞争对手感到不满，他们认为对最终出现的政府没有什么乐观的理由。在上周投票没有结果后，该国两个最大的政党目前正在就总理职位进行谈判。面对需要在主要由无党派人士主导的议会中组建联盟的情况，各党派正在应对选举后情况带来的挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/seen-from-abroad-pakistan-elections-disappoint-add-to-instability/articleshow/107657523.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯为何要修建30公里长的“沙皇列车”屏障</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/why-russia-is-building-a-30-km-long-tsar-train-barrier/articleshow/107656727.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107656727.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:15:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/why-russia-is-building-a-30-km-long-tsar-train-barrier/articleshow/107656727.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称俄罗斯空袭损坏了第聂伯罗电厂</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-air-attack-damages-dnipro-power-plant-ukraine-says/articleshow/107656886.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107656886.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰官员和媒体称，俄罗斯周二用导弹和无人机袭击了乌克兰中部城市第聂伯罗，摧毁了一座发电厂，迫使当局关闭学校并疏散医院。乌克兰空军在 Telegram 消息应用程序上表示，这座人口接近 100 万的城市遭到了来自南部、东部和北部的一枚导弹和四组无人机的攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:08:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-air-attack-damages-dnipro-power-plant-ukraine-says/articleshow/107656886.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国制裁四名被控在约旦河西岸侵犯人权的以色列定居者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sanctions-4-israeli-settlers-accused-of-human-rights-abuses-in-west-bank/articleshow/107657096.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107657096.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国政府对四名被指控侵犯约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人人权的以色列定居者实施制裁。制裁包括资产冻结以及旅行和签证禁令。美国总统乔·拜登此前对参与袭击巴勒斯坦人的其他四名定居者实施了类似的制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:18:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sanctions-4-israeli-settlers-accused-of-human-rights-abuses-in-west-bank/articleshow/107657096.cms</guid></item><item><title>两名亚美尼亚士兵被阿塞拜疆炮火打死，这是会谈开始以来的第一起重大事件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-armenian-soldiers-killed-by-azerbaijani-fire-in-first-major-incident-since-talks-began/articleshow/107655790.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107655790.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亚美尼亚国防部在 Telegram 消息应用程序上发布的一份声明中表示，在亚美尼亚南部村庄 Nerkin Hand 附近的一个战斗哨所，两名士兵被杀，多人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 08:34:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-armenian-soldiers-killed-by-azerbaijani-fire-in-first-major-incident-since-talks-began/articleshow/107655790.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国农民联盟主席表示抗议活动可能会恢复</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/head-of-french-farmers-union-says-protests-could-resume/articleshow/107655248.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107655248.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;政府正在与农民进行谈判，以提高他们向超市的销售价格，并放松监管和官僚主义，农民称这些对他们的企业造成了负担。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 08:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/head-of-french-farmers-union-says-protests-could-resume/articleshow/107655248.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国农民联盟主席表示抗议活动可能会恢复</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/head-of-french-farmers-union-says-protests-could-resume/articleshow/107654876.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107654876.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 08:06:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/head-of-french-farmers-union-says-protests-could-resume/articleshow/107654876.cms</guid></item><item><title>总统办公室称斯里兰卡将于2025年举行大选</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lankas-general-election-to-be-held-in-2025-says-presidents-office/articleshow/107652293.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107652293.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 07:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lankas-general-election-to-be-held-in-2025-says-presidents-office/articleshow/107652293.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促以色列“尽快”停止在拉法的军事行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/china-urges-israel-to-stop-military-operation-in-rafah-as-soon-as-possible/articleshow/107653204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107653204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国周二敦促以色列“尽快”停止在加沙城市拉法的军事行动，并警告称，如果战斗不停止，那里将发生“严重的人道主义灾难”。北京敦促以色列“尽快停止军事行动，并尽一切努力避免无辜平民伤亡，防止拉法地区发生更严重的人道主义灾难”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 07:17:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/china-urges-israel-to-stop-military-operation-in-rafah-as-soon-as-possible/articleshow/107653204.cms</guid></item><item><title>致命骚乱后巴布亚新几内亚总理将面临议会不信任动议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/papua-new-guinea-pm-to-face-no-confidence-motion-in-parliament-after-deadly-riots/articleshow/107651331.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107651331.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴布亚新几内亚反对党在一月份警察罢工期间发生致命骚乱后，向总理詹姆斯·马拉佩提出了不信任动议。马拉佩表示有信心击败该动议。这个太平洋上最大的岛国已与美国签署了防务合作协议，并受到中国的安全关系欢迎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 06:25:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/papua-new-guinea-pm-to-face-no-confidence-motion-in-parliament-after-deadly-riots/articleshow/107651331.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普支持儿媳担任共和党全国委员会联合主席</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-endorses-his-daughter-in-law-lara-trump-as-co-chair-of-the-republican-national-committee/articleshow/107651106.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107651106.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;共和党全国委员会现任主席罗娜·麦克丹尼尔(Ronna McDaniel)因选举表现平平和筹款金额平淡而受到批评。与此同时，唐纳德·特朗普对其儿媳劳拉·特朗普和迈克尔·沃特利的支持加强了他对共和党竞选机构的控制。 RNC 在 2023 年筹集了 8700 万美元，年底手头现金为 800 万美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 06:21:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-endorses-his-daughter-in-law-lara-trump-as-co-chair-of-the-republican-national-committee/articleshow/107651106.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何从拉法手中救出两名人质</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-rescue-2-hostages-from-rafah-in-dramatic-gaza-raid-news/articleshow/107648191.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107648191.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特警队的准备工作可能包括数周的排练，重点是进入战术和处理人口稠密地区的复杂情况。在与哈马斯持续冲突的情况下，人质成功获救鼓舞了以色列人的士气。然而，这次袭击加剧了加沙的人道主义危机，并凸显了从冲突地区解救人质的风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 05:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-forces-rescue-2-hostages-from-rafah-in-dramatic-gaza-raid-news/articleshow/107648191.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国的厄运循环：人口大幅减少（且老龄化）可能会造成毁灭性的全球经济放缓</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-doom-loop-a-dramatically-smaller-and-older-population-could-create-a-devastating-global-slowdown/articleshow/107648308.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107648308.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;这种转变可能会产生一些相互关联的经济后果，最终影响中国的中长期经济福祉，并在全球范围内引起共鸣。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 05:21:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-doom-loop-a-dramatically-smaller-and-older-population-could-create-a-devastating-global-slowdown/articleshow/107648308.cms</guid></item><item><title>由于酷热，奥克兰火车服务中断</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/train-services-disrupted-in-auckland-due-to-extreme-heat/articleshow/107647100.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107647100.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;奥克兰的酷热导致火车服务中断和延误。奥克兰人因天气变化、信号故障和其他问题而感到沮丧。该市正在寻求迅速解决方案，以确保居民的交通顺畅可靠。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 04:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/train-services-disrupted-in-auckland-due-to-extreme-heat/articleshow/107647100.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>